---
description: UI boundary rules
globs:
  - "src/components/**/*.tsx"
  - "src/modules/**/ui/**/*.tsx"
  - "src/modules/**/components/**/*.tsx"
  - "src/modules/control/pages/**/*.tsx"
alwaysApply: false
---

# UI Boundaries

- Do not import Supabase clients, repositories, or storage services in UI components.
- Do not add direct `localStorage` access to UI components.
- UI should call application hooks or receive callbacks from containers.
- Loading and error states from async persistence must be represented by hook state, not hidden inside render-time side effects.
